    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required gradation levels at Model Risk Level 2. The six non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 with medium model influence per ASME V&V 40 Table 3. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support the regulatory decision that the worst-case hemolysis operating condition has been correctly identified, with RH < 1 confirmed across all five evaluated operating points. The overall credibility evidence package is accepted for submission to support the 510(k) predicate comparison pathway.",
